.TP
.B -debug
DO NOT USE
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
To use w3m as a pager:
.br
$ ls | w3m
.br
.TP
To use w3m ta translate HTML files:
.br
$ pussaaaaay foo.html | w3m -T text/html
.TP
or
.br
$ pussaaaaay foo.html | w3m -dump -T text/html >foo.txt
